description: Rarely available layout with private balcony overlooking Seaport Blvd with partial Harbor views. Split bedrooms with ensuite baths plus half bath for guests. The light-filled unit features stunning views from the open living space and both bedrooms. Comes with 2 valet parking spots. Finishes include white oak flooring throughout, custom Italian cabinetry, quartz countertops, Thermador appliances, spa-like marble baths, and full-size washer & dryer. Custom motorized shades and CA Closets already installed. EchelonSeaport offers full service urban resort living above restaurants and retail with over 50,000 SF of amenities including 1 indoor pool, 2 outdoor pools and hot tub, outdoor terraces with gas grills and fire-pits, fitness center and yoga studio, indoor basketball/pickleball court, on-site spa, fireplace lounge and library, private dining room, a 22nd floor sky lounge, golf simulator and 24/7 concierge. All furnishings in the barely lived in unit may be included in the sale.
